<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Success</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your custom styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
        }

        .info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
        }
        .authority {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #888;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Registration Successful!</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= Name %>,</p>
        <p>We are thrilled to welcome you to our platform. Your registration was successful!</p>
        <div class="info">
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
            <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> <%= PhoneNum %></p>
            <p><strong>One Time Password (OTP):</strong> <%= userOTP %></p>
        </div>
        <p>We hope you enjoy your experience with us!</p>
        <div class="authority">
            <p><em>This email was sent by Ecoco, the authorized platform owner.</em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
